                        <interp inst="t18381022-name-1173" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>HENRY HART</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a constable of Merton. I apprehended the prisoner—the two witnesses were running after him—I found the handkerchief three or four yards from the prisoner in a hedge—I saw him stoop down to the spot.</p>
               <p>
